  "description" : "* Based on a stand-up comedy shounen manga written by http://anidb.net/cr82616 [Suenaga Yuuki] and drawn by http://anidb.net/cr82617 [Moue Takamasa].\nRakugo--the ultimate form of storytelling, where everything in a story is expressed with just your body and words. http://anidb.net/ch154287 [Shinta] and his daughter http://anidb.net/ch150183 [Akane] have been seduced by this wonderful form of classical entertainment. Having observed her father strive to pass the shin`uchi rakugo test, Akane will take her own steps into this unique world!\nSource: Manga Plus",
